---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Member card — Mary Jane's Place"
  description="About the Mary Jane's Place digital member card: QR verification, PDF download, and wallet support."
>
  <section class="ph-top pad-sm">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <div class="eyebrow kick rv">Member card</div>
      <h1 class="rv">Your digital member card.</h1>
      <p class="rv lede" style="margin-top:14px">
        Every member gets a digital card with a QR code. Show it at the counter — staff scan the QR to confirm your Member ID.
      </p>

      <div class="rv" style="margin-top:18px;border-top:1px solid var(--line)">
        <details class="acc-item" open>
          <summary>How do I use it?</summary>
          <div>Open your card on your phone (or print the PDF) and show the QR at the counter. Staff scan it to pull up your Member ID and tier.</div>
        </details>
        <details class="acc-item">
          <summary>Can I download it?</summary>
          <div>Yes — use "Download as PDF" on your card. The PDF carries the same QR and details, so a printed copy works just as well.</div>
        </details>
        <details class="acc-item">
          <summary>Apple Wallet / Google Wallet?</summary>
          <div>Wallet passes are coming in a later update. For now, save your card to your phone or keep the PDF handy. The "Add to Wallet" buttons link here until that's live.</div>
        </details>
        <details class="acc-item">
          <summary>Do I need a physical card?</summary>
          <div>No. The digital card and QR are all you need. There are no plastic cards in this version.</div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <div class="rv" style="margin-top:26px;display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap">
        <a class="btn" href="/join">Join <span class="arr">→</span></a>
        <a class="btn ghost" href="/membership">About membership</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .acc-item { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .acc-item summary {
    list-style: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 18px 2px;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 16px; align-items: center;
    font-family: var(--font); font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--olive-d);
  }
  .acc-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .acc-item summary::after {
    content: "+"; flex: none; width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--line); display: grid; place-items: center;
    transition: 0.25s; font-size: 17px; color: var(--olive); line-height: 1;
  }
  .acc-item[open] summary::after { background: var(--olive); border-color: var(--olive); color: #fff; transform: rotate(45deg); }
  .acc-item > div { padding: 0 2px 18px; color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 16px; max-width: 74ch; }
</style>
